   4  SCALAR IBALVERSN 'This version of Balmorel' /403.20220318/;
   5  * Efforts have been made to make a good model.
   6  * However, most probably the model is incomplete and subject to errors.
   7  * It is distributed with the idea that it will be usefull anyway,
   8  * and with the purpose of getting the essential feedback,
   9  * which in turn will permit the development of improved versions
  10  * to the benefit of other user.
  11  * Hopefully it will be applied in that spirit.
  12   
